@title IMAP UTF-7 encoding/decoding library
@reference See <a href="https://github.com/DOBRO/erlang-imap-utf7" target="_blank">imap_utf7 page on github</a> for more information and examples.

@doc The library provides functions for encoding/decoding Erlang UTF-8 binaries to and from modified UTF-7 encoding
in accordance with <a href="https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc3501#section-5.1.3" target="_blank">RFC 3501, section section 5.1.3.</a>
